# CateringPromo Component Rules

## Overview
Rules for `src/components/organisms/CateringPromo.tsx`

## Purpose
Organism that composes promo image and copy into a two-column responsive section.

## Rules
- ✅ Layout: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center`.
- ✅ Composition: Uses `PromoImage` atom and `CateringPromoCopy` molecule.
- ✅ Data Source: Image src/alt/aspect from `CATERING_PROMO.image` in `@/constants/catering`.
- ✅ Semantics: Wrap in `<section className="w-full">`.
- ✅ No local strings; all copy in constants.

## Template
```tsx
<PromoImage src={CATERING_PROMO.image.src} alt={CATERING_PROMO.image.alt} aspectRatio={CATERING_PROMO.image.aspectRatio} />
<CateringPromoCopy />
```

## Responsive Behavior
- 1 column on mobile, 2 columns from `md:`.
- Gaps: `gap-8` mobile, `md:gap-12` desktop.

## QA Checklist
- Renders image with correct alt.
- Heading and copy match constants.
- CTA navigates to the expected href.
- Layout stacks on mobile and splits on desktop.